openjsip.remote.locationservice

Class Binding

  • java.lang.Object
    • openjsip.remote.locationservice.Binding
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Binding
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Binding represents association between public address of subscriber and the current IP where it can be contacted.
